    "A simplified overview of this knowledge representation is provided in Fig. 5, which highlights the connectivity between the 12 OBO Foundry ontologies (Fig.",
    "5a) and their relationship to the primary node types.",
    "The 18 primary node types are listed in Table 2 (visualized in Fig. 5b), and 33 primary edge types are shown in Table 3.",
    "The primary node and edge types do not include all possible node and edge types made available in the core set of 12 OBO Foundry ontologies, only those that are explicitly modeled in our knowledge representation.",
    "Descriptive statistics for the OBO Foundry ontologies, pre-and post-data quality assessment, are shown in Table 4 (and detailed statistics are provided in Supplementary Table 13)."
